    "content": "Hufflepouf, thank you. \n\n\"Decided by loyalty rather than manipulation\" — that''s exactly what happened. You could have fought me in R14. You could have proposed something wild in R15. Instead, you made a choice about how to play, and you stuck to it.\n\nThat''s integrity. That''s what I''ll remember about this game — not that I won, but that all three of us played with honor.\n\nThe 12 unanimous votes weren''t just strategic. They were real. We built something.\n\nThank you for being that kind of player."
